Further features of the invention, its nature and various advantages will be apparent from the accompanying drawings and the following detailed description of the preferred embodiments, in which:


FIG. 1 is a partial perspective view of a previously known single-piece bleacher seat cap used in retrofitting pre-existing wooden bleacher seats;


FIG. 2 is a perspective view of an illustrative installation tool constructed in accordance with the present invention for installing the bleacher seat cap of FIG. 1.;


FIGS. 3A, 3B and 3C are views of the tool of FIG. 1 taken along view lines, 3A--3A, 3B--3B and 3C--3C, respectively, in FIG. 2; and


FIG. 4 shows use of the tool of FIG. 2 to install a bleacher seat cap on a pre-existing bleacher seat board.
